{"tid":527049,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【要封殺？】南韓財長：各部門對加密貨幣管制共識一致！","createTime":"2018-01-12T09:12:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T09:12:31.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c21b6edd09005da4b990c75c0f7bbea63d82d296","tid":527049,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T09:12:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180112/large/1515746190_ad51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180112%2Flarge%2F1515746190_ad51.jpg&h=e1cb59d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前傳出南韓計劃禁止加密貨幣交易，令比特幣（Bitcoin）價格一度急挫。據《韓聯社》報道，南韓副總理兼財長金東兗表示，各部門一致認為政府需對加密貨幣交易投機過熱，採取措施，並給予合理的管制。<br />\n<br />\n金東兗說昨日司法部提出關閉加密貨幣交易所方案，應與有關部門進行磋商。他又指區塊鏈技術，是第四次工業革命基礎技術之一，與保安、物流等不少產業有密切關係，必須全面且客觀對待。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180112/57699129\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180112%2F57699129&d=ZLlp%2BqdNaSGF4Tu9lAAn4dWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=ad6dce2d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180112%2F57699129&h=98428ced\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180112/57699129</a>"}]}